<div id="pf43bc" class="pf w4f h303" data-page-no="43bc"><div class="pc pc43bc w4f h303"><div class="t m2c0 xef h5 y2f41 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 1 April 1-7 </div><div class="t m69b x11 h5 y239c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Knowing the time, that now it is </div><div class="t m7d4 x3 h5 y2315 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">high time to awake out of sleep: </div><div class="t m9be xbd h5 y1fb9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for now is our salvation nearer than </div><div class="t m7bf x3 h5 y6c7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">when we believed. . . . Let us walk </div><div class="t mc8 x3 h5 y807 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">honestly, as in the day. . . . Put </div><div class="t me02 x3 h5 y1fe6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ye on the Lord Jesus Christ, and make </div><div class="t m1b5 x3 h5 yb07 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not provision for the flesh, to </div><div class="t m134c xbd h5 ya0c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fulfil the lusts thereof&quot; (Rom. </div><div class="t m67 x3 h5 y3ca ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13:11-14). </div><div class="t m8ba x11 h35 y1097 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The events of the last days are of </div><div class="t m3a9 xbd h35 yb09 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">such importance that their careful </div><div class="t meab xbd h35 y580 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study is essential for every child of </div><div class="t m2c5 xbd h35 y567 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. The end of the investigative </div><div class="t m132c xbd h35 y14bb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">judgment, which is the end of </div><div class="t mbde xbd h35 y1524 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">probationary time, and the second </div><div class="t m2aa xbd h35 y8b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coming of Christ will surprise many </div><div class="t ma80 xbd h35 y18a2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">professed Christians. This is why we </div><div class="t m4b7 xbd h35 y1321 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">find this admonition: &quot;Behold, I come </div><div class="t m62a xbd h35 y821 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as a thief. Blessed is he that watcheth, </div><div class="t m16c xbd h35 y15f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and keepeth his garments, lest he </div><div class="t m180 xbd h35 yd22 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">walk naked, and they see his shame&quot; </div><div class="t m417 xbd h35 ye85 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:15). </div><div class="t m335 x11 h35 yd33 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We watch by studying the precious </div><div class="t m1af xbd h35 y3a4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">messages God has left for us in His </div><div class="t mdcc xbd h35 y41a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Word and in the spirit of prophecy </div><div class="t m816 xbd h35 y546 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">writings, by secret prayer, by a </div><div class="t mf22 xbd h35 y4b1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">daily surrender to Christ, and by </div><div class="t m656 xbd h35 y784 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">application of God&apos;s messages to our </div><div class="t m144c xbd h35 y8c1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individual lives. </div><div class="t ma6 x11 h35 y21b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The great happenings foretold in </div><div class="t m54e xbd h35 y12e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophecy have a definite relation with </div><div class="t m4b3 xbd h35 y1131 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">each other. Most church members </div><div class="t m586 xbd h35 y706 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have studied these things at one time </div><div class="t ma81 xbd h35 yc57 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">or another, but sometimes they do not </div><div class="t m9b7 xbd h35 y72d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have a clear idea about the sequence </div><div class="t m41a xbd h35 y910 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in which the events will come, and </div><div class="t m850 xbd h35 y37f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this makes the whole picture confused </div><div class="t mbe2 xbd h35 y11f0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to them. </div><div class="t m173d x17 h35 y40f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is our purpose in this first lesson </div><div class="t m6fe xbd h35 ycc5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to present these main issues in their </div><div class="t m459 xbd h35 y1ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chronological order and to show them </div><div class="t maf1 xbd h35 y8da ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in an overview. We will give just </div><div class="t mac9 xbd h35 ya34 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a brief explanation of the nature of </div><div class="t m533 xbd h35 yfbe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">each one of them, and later we will </div><div class="t ma6b xbd h35 y6dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">examine each one in more depth. </div><div class="t m845 x17 h35 y153b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Many of us have seen charts of the </div><div class="t m862 xbd h35 y3e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">final events showing the exact  </div><div class="t m344 x6e h35 y2348 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sequence of many details. But can </div><div class="t m1168 x6e h35 y1584 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">any particular order be sustained by </div><div class="t m80f x6e h35 y15f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the inspired pen? Notice that in this </div><div class="t m7b6 x6e h35 y385 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study we have not tried to fit every </div><div class="t m8ba x6e h35 y592 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">detail into exact sequence. </div><div class="t m740 x86 h35 y2084 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the chart on page 114 (see page </div><div class="t m70d x6e h35 y819 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16 of Teacher&apos;s Quarterly) we place </div><div class="t m6ad x6e h35 ya5a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only the main issues in a logical </div><div class="t ma43 x6e h35 yf69 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sequence, leaving out of the picture </div><div class="t m70a x6e h35 y1227 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">any hypothesis or personal opinion </div><div class="t m7ba xbc h35 y4a6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">regarding the less important </div><div class="t m5a9 x6e h35 y1539 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">occurrences, or those whose exact </div><div class="t m4a3 x6e h35 y927 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">order has not been revealed to us. </div><div class="t m19 x6e h35 yfb9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This chart is brief and clear, and </div><div class="t m9d2 xbc h35 y610 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">every item can be easily verified in the </div><div class="t ma33 xbc h35 y900 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible or in Ellen White&apos;s writings. </div><div class="t mb1a x86 h35 y112d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">May this overview help us to know </div><div class="t m35d xbc h35 y1254 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the time. May it prompt us to awake </div><div class="t m65b x6e h35 y3fd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from spiritual sleep. May it lead us to </div><div class="t m82f xbc h35 y153a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">put on now the Lord Jesus Christ, </div><div class="t m61c xbc h35 y46d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the only source of strength and safety </div><div class="t m5a3 xbc h35 y2112 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the trouble-filled days that separate </div><div class="t m130d xbc h35 yfe6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us from the glorious hour of the </div><div class="t me8b xbc h35 y809 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coming of the Saviour. </div><div class="t m4d6 xbc h5 y7bc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f xbc h5 y3bf ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5af xab h5 y3bf ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Events During Probation—I </div><div class="t m220 x8 h5 ya6c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Amos 9:9) </div><div class="t m558 xbc h5 y128a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m635 xab h5 y9c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Events During Probation—II </div><div class="t mcdb x8 h5 y867 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. </div><div class="t m335 x76 h35 y810 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7:3) </div><div class="t mb7 xbc h5 y675 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m7d0 xab h5 y54e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Events During Probation—III </div><div class="t mf53 x8 h5 y3b1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 13:15-17) </div><div class="t m1ce xbc h5 y78d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m4c9 xab h5 y19f1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Time of Trouble </div><div class="t m481 x8 h5 y7c2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Dan. 12:1) </div><div class="t m8a8 xbc h5 ya09 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m43e x8 h5 y32a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Events During the Time of Trouble </div><div class="t m455 x8 h5 y32 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:1-21) </div><div class="t m2ef xbc h5 y1132 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m307 xab h5 y16f0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Events From Liberation of </div><div class="t mb0f x8 h5 y4d9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Saints to the </div><div class="t m20d x8 h5 yb24 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second Advent (Rev. 12:11) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
